snippet.description:
The Official Video for PinkPantheress, Ice Spice - Boy's a liar pt 2. Out now: https://PinkPantheress.lnk.to/BALPt2 

Follow PinkPantheress:
IG - https://www.instagram.com/pinkpantheress

Lyrics

PinkPantheress: 
take a look inside your heart 
is there any room for me
i won’t ever have to hold my breath 
till you get down on one knee 
because 
you only want to hold me when i’m looking good enough
did you ever feel me 
could you ever picture us 

every time i pull my hair 
well it’s only our of fear 
that you’ll find me ugly 
and one day you’ll disappear
because 
what’s the point of crying it was never even love
did you ever want me was i ever good enough 
 
the boys a liar 
the boys a liar 
he doesn’t see you 
you’re not looking at me boy 
the boys a liar 
the boys a liar 
he doesn’t see you 
you’re not looking at me boy 

good enough nough nough
good enough nough nough
good enough nough nough
good enough nough nough

Ice Spice: 

he say that I’m good enough 
grabbin’ my duhduhduh
thinkin’ bout shit that I shouldn’ta 
so I tell him there’s one of me 
he making fun of me, his girl is a bum to me 
like that boy is a cap, saying he home but I know where he at like
bet he’s blowing her back, thinking bout me cos he knows that it’s fat
and it been what it been, calling his phone like “yo send me a pin”
ducking my shit cus he know what I’m on 
but when he hit me Im not gon’ respond 
but I don’t sleep enough without you 
and I can’t eat enough without you 
if we don’t speak does that mean we’re through?
don’t like sneaky shit that you do 

PinkPantheress: 

the boys a liar 
the boys a liar 
he doesn’t see you 
you’re not looking at me boy 
the boys a liar 
the boys a liar 
he doesn’t see you 
you’re not looking at me boy 

good enough nough nough
good enough nough nough
good enough nough nough
good enough nough nough
good enough nough nough
good enough nough nough

snippet.title: Tiny House Swap with Eva zu Beck
snippet.description:
We trade tiny homes for 24 hours to answer: VAN LIFE OR OVERLANDING?! Subscribe to @EvazuBeckOfficial & watch how her #vanlife day unfolded. To get a 1 year supply of Vitamin D + 10 travel packs FREE with your first purchase, go to https://athleticgreens.com/eamonandbec

0:00 van life vs. overlanding
0:51 tour Eva's setup
5:14 first drive in the Land Rover 😬 
8:23 AG special!
10:37 I'm causing a scene 🙈
12:45 where we park overnight in mexico
15:01 cooking = camping 
19:07 bedroom setup in the 4X4
22:06 no toilet but I have to go 💩 
23:04 final thoughts 🚐 vs. 🛻

I've often wondered what it would be like to downsize our tiny home to a truck conversion that takes you anywhere you want to go!  On the flip side, our friend Eva has wondered what it'd be like to upgrade her sq-ft to something a little bit bigger (like a van) that can accommodate a toilet, shower, and some extra storage/living space. TODAY, we switch lives for 24 hours and do a TINY HOUSE SWAP!!! Watch until the end of the video to hear all of our thoughts on each other's alternative lifestyles and which option we would VOTE for: van life or overlanding?

snippet.title: Emanuel Navarrete & Liam Wilson Have Fight of the Year, Both Get Dropped, Navarrete Gets KO Win in 9
snippet.description:
Watch highlights from the main event of #navarretewilson featuring #emanuelnavarrete and Liam Wilson. In what will be the fight of the year, this back and forth affair had everything. Both men get dropped before Navarrete finishes Wilson in Round 9. 

Next for Top Rank Boxing,  Most Valuable Promotions (MVP) announced that international superstar Jake “The Problem Child” Paul will, at long last, face undefeated pro boxer Tommy “TNT” Fury, younger brother of Heavyweight World Champion Tyson Fury, in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia on Sunday, February 26, 2023.

Paul vs. Fury will stream live on ESPN+ PPV (2PM ET / 11AM PT), the exclusive digital distributor in the United States. Additionally, it will be available via cable and satellite pay-per-view providers and will be priced at $49.99

snippet.title: Resident Evil 4 Remake: Exclusive Chapter 5 Gameplay Walkthrough
snippet.description:
The Resident Evil 4 remake is Game Informer’s cover story for February, and as part of our ongoing features, we’re sharing an extended gameplay walkthrough of the game’s fifth chapter, set right after Leon meets Ashley. 

Marcus Stewart, and Alex Van Aken played this chapter at Capcom’s headquarters for our cover story. You'll get a great look at the section we played as well as our commentary for added context. The footage includes extended looks at the church and cemetery sequences, a demonstration of combat and exploration, capping off with a larger slice of the chaotic cabin battle with Luis Serra. 

Disclaimer: Capcom helped to arrange and cover travel accommodations for two in Osaka, Japan, in association with this cover story. As the world’s largest video game magazine, Game Informer’s editorial team is proud to remain impartial, professional, and committed to the truth in all forms of our content, regardless of this circumstance.

snippet.title: Bryan Cranston Fully Commits While Eating Spicy Wings | Hot Ones
snippet.description:
Bryan Cranston is a six-time Emmy Award–winning actor you know from acclaimed Broadway performances, films that include 2013's Best Picture Argo, and iconic TV shows like Malcolm in the Middle and Breaking Bad. He also stars in the highly anticipated second season of the crime drama Your Honor, now airing on Showtime. But how is he with spicy food? Find out as he makes his triumphant return to the Hot Ones table and takes on the wings of death with Sean Evans. Along the way, he discusses his love affair with the Dodgers, behind-the-scenes Breaking Bad stories, and the keys to being a committed actor.
